OL,3,CCalls for South West Water CEO to
OL,4,Cresign over 'Christmas sewage dumping'
OL,6,FThe boss of South West Water has been
OL,7,Ftold to resign by a group of MPs
OL,8,Fciting Christmas sewage dumping,
OL,9,Frising bills, and poor service
OL,10,Fdelivery.
OL,12,FSusan Davy, who is CEO of Pennon Group
OL,13,F- South West Water's parent company -
OL,14,Fhas been urged to "do the decent
OL,15,Fthing" and step down from her #860,000-
OL,16,Fa-year job by three South West MPs.
OL,26,@vD@SOUwD@FO]
