OL,3,CCalls for South West Water CEO to
OL,4,Cresign over 'Christmas sewage dumping'
OL,6,FThe letter was sent by Ben Maguire,
OL,7,Fthe Liberal Democrats MP for North
OL,8,FCornwall, and co-signed by Andrew
OL,9,FGeorge, the Liberal Democrats MP for
OL,10,FSt Ives, and Cameron Thomas, the
OL,11,FLiberal Democrat MP for Tewkesbury.
OL,13,FNeil Duncan-Jordan, the Labour MP for
OL,14,FPoole, was a fourth signatory.
