OL,3,CCalls for South West Water CEO to
OL,4,Cresign over 'Christmas sewage dumping'
OL,6,F"We are writing to you directly to
OL,7,Fcall for your resignation as Chief
OL,8,FExecutive of Pennon Group following
OL,9,Fyour company's repeated and
OL,10,Funacceptable failures to prevent
OL,11,Fsewage dumping across Cornwall and the
OL,12,FSouth West's beaches and waterways,"
OL,13,FMr Maguire said in his letter.
OL,15,F"The scale of the crisis under your
OL,16,Fleadership is now intolerable.
