OL,3,CCalls for South West Water CEO to
OL,4,Cresign over 'Christmas sewage dumping'
OL,6,F"The Environment Agency reported a
OL,7,Fstaggering 530,000+ hours of sewage
OL,8,Foverflows in the south-west region in
OL,9,F2023 alone, an 83% increase on the
OL,10,Fprevious year."
OL,12,FIn their letter, the MPs accused
OL,13,FPennon Group of increasing water bills
OL,14,Fwhile "the standards of service that
OL,15,Four constituents feel they receive
OL,16,Fdrops lower and lower by the day".
OL,18,F'We deserve better than this' - MPs
OL,26,@rD@OO]vD@GOUxD@aO]
