OL,3,CCalls for South West Water CEO to
OL,4,Cresign over 'Christmas sewage dumping'
OL,6,FThey added: "Adding insult to injury,
OL,7,Fyour decision to forgo a bonus but
OL,8,Finstead increase your total
OL,9,Fcompensation from #543,000 to #860,000
OL,10,Fdoes nothing to reassure us that you
OL,11,Ftake these failures seriously.
OL,13,F"For the sake of our constituents, for
OL,14,Fall of the South West, and for the
OL,15,Fenvironment we hold so dear, I urge
OL,16,Fyou to do the decent thing and step
OL,17,Faside, so that fresh leadership can
OL,18,Ffinally rectify the scandal of sewage
OL,19,Fdumping.
OL,21,F"We deserve better than this."
