OL,3,CCalls for South West Water CEO to
OL,4,Cresign over 'Christmas sewage dumping'
OL,6,FSouth West Water serves approximately
OL,7,F1.8 million people living in Cornwall,
OL,8,FDevon, and parts of Somerset and
OL,9,FDorset.
OL,11,FThe company was acquired by Pennon
OL,12,FGroup in June 2024, which Ms Davy
OL,13,Foversaw as part of a wider acquisition
OL,14,Fof Bournemouth Water, Bristol Water,
OL,15,FSutton, and East Surrey Water.
OL,17,FSouth West Water, which has been
OL,18,Fapproached by ITV News West Country
OL,19,Ffor comment, say it remains committed
OL,20,Fto improving water quality for its
OL,21,Fcustomers.
